                          |CKOPack Talk
|GKO================================================================

|YKOPack talk sends a message to all members of your pack
currently on Darkwind. It is essentially the same
as talking on a channel that only your pack can see.

|WKOUsable in forms: |GKOAll
|WKOSyntax:|YKB pt <message>         |WKOCost: |CKOFree
